 Syntax:  .set desc <description>

Results:  Provides a description beside your name that can be seen when
          using the .look and .who commands and when you sign on and off the
          board. <description> is the description you choose to have.
          To view your current description, type .set desc by itself.

Example:  To set it to "likes to have fun" type:
	  .set desc likes to have fun 

See also:  look, who
